{"tid":2392641,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇返工兄弟做緊間公司嘅屙屎風氣好差？","createTime":"2021-02-03T02:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T01:28:25.000Z","uid":40930,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"898585008284bdc53ea116cfbafb4c94e36a10da","tid":2392641,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:23:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老味真係不撚知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前fg 第一份濕鳩工得個10k 、又要長短週返shift，都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得閒去下廁所屙屎，到返埋位時啲同事就啤啤啤、死肥佬上司又會俾下面色你睇，然後問下你去咗邊咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣結果搞到公司成陣白色恐怖味，去屙屎都好似有罪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你啦，你地返工個陣未咇撚過屎呀？唔講仲以為因為我去咗屙屎搞到公司赤字<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上而家公司出錢請我返嚟係做嘢？傻撚咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後做咗幾個月冇做了，而家人工係個間on99公司嘅幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屙屎風氣仲好咗，至少去屙幾耐都冇人理，自由的風<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96152097889d634964268dbc788e39143325ad96","tid":2392641,"uid":44854,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"Cls呢d公司走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日最少柯3次，每次15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d327c5d3c9bd4e1e99410d03cf134a0e9e7b4d5c","tid":2392641,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:28:28.000Z","msg":"廁格=食煙區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba908535d28af3c38bd409f02f2b088dd62f7fa0","tid":2392641,"uid":113929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T02:34:58.000Z","msg"